Our offer - Alfred Berg



































































 
 









 


Home / Our offer





 
Our offer We offer asset management services through our existing Alfred Berg and BNP Paribas Asset Management fund range, but we also manage assets on the behalf of foreign funds holding Nordic, Eastern European and Russian assets. Examples of the latter are funds in Japan, Korea, Luxembourg, Belgium and France.
Our funds
Our range of investment solutions spans the market cap and style spectrum and reaches from regional and global equity and fixed income strategies to multi-asset products. In addition to Alfred Berg’s own extensive range of investment solutions, we are the sole distributor of BNP Paribas Asset Management’s investment products and services in Finland, Norway and Sweden.
Read more about what specific funds you can invest in on the local Alfred Berg web pages in local languages.

